data.description: Welcome to this exquisite home that seamlessly blends timeless elegance with modern functionality. As you step inside, the warm and inviting atmosphere of the living spaces is immediately apparent, thanks to the rich maple wood flooring that graces the main level and beautifully preserved woodwork throughout. The luxurious vinyl flooring in select areas adds a touch of contemporary sophistication, creating a perfect balance between classic charm and contemporary style. Convenience meets practicality with the second-floor laundry room. No more lugging laundry up and down stairs; this home is designed for optimal ease and comfort. Storage is abundant throughout, ensuring that every item has its designated place, maintaining the home's pristine appearance. The walk-in closet is a fashion enthusiast's dream, providing ample space for an organized wardrobe and making getting ready a pleasure. Indulge in the convenience of a butler pantry that doubles as a sophisticated coffee bar. Whether hosting guests or enjoying a quiet morning, this space is designed to cater to your every need. Schedule your viewing of this beautiful home today!
